name: trange
description: Filters time-series data for the given time range.

params.name: start_time_or_interval
params.description: Time interval or start time value for single parameter mode. Start time for two parameter mode.  In two parameter mode, the start time value can be a date string or epoch milliseconds.

params.name: start_time_or_interval
params.description: Time interval or start time value for single parameter mode. Start time for two parameter mode.  In two parameter mode, the start time value can be a date string or epoch milliseconds.

params.name: start_time_or_interval
params.description: Time interval or start time value for single parameter mode. Start time for two parameter mode.  In two parameter mode, the start time value can be a date string or epoch milliseconds.

params.name: end_time
params.description: Explicit end time that can be a date string or epoch milliseconds, or a modifier for the first parameter. The modifier can be a time duration or date period.

examples:
FROM k8s
| WHERE TRANGE("2024-05-10T00:17:14.000Z")
| SORT @timestamp
| KEEP @timestamp
| LIMIT 10

FROM k8s
| WHERE TRANGE(1715300236000)
| SORT @timestamp
| KEEP @timestamp
| LIMIT 10

FROM k8s
| WHERE TRANGE("2024-05-10T00:17:14.000Z", "2024-05-10T00:18:33.000Z")
| SORT @timestamp
| KEEP @timestamp
| LIMIT 10

FROM k8s
